one&#39;s progress. You cannot use reverse of=\r\n f(x, y) to gauge x, without knowing y.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div align=3D&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;f=\r\nont color=3D&quot;#000000&quot; size=3D&quot;2&quot; face=3D&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;=A0&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div ali=\r\ngn=3D&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=3D&quot;#000000&quot; size=3D&quot;2&quot; face=3D&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;Best regard=\r\ns,&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div align=3D&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=3D&quot;#000000&quot; size=3D&quot;2&quot; face=\r\n=3D&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;Narasimha&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div align=3D&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=3D&quot;#000=\r\n000&quot; size=3D&quot;2&quot; face=3D&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;------------------------------------------=\r\n-------------------------&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div align=3D&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=3D&quot;#=\r\n000000&quot; size=3D&quot;2&quot; face=3D&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;=A0 Free Jyotish Software, Free Jyotish=\r\n Lessons, Jyotish Writings,&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div align=3D&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=3D=\r\n&quot;#000000&quot; size=3D&quot;2&quot; face=3D&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;&quot;Do It Yourself&quot; ritual man=\r\nuals for short Homam and Pitri Tarpana:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div align=3D&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;f=\r\nont color=3D&quot;#000000&quot; size=3D&quot;2&quot; face=3D&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;=A0=A0=A0=A0=A0=A0=A0=A0=\r\n=A0=A0=A0=A0=A0=A0=A0=A0=A0 &lt;a href=3D&quot;http://www.vedicastrologer.org/&quot; tar=\r\nget=3D&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://www.VedicAstrologer.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div align=\r\n=3D&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=3D&quot;#000000&quot; size=3D&quot;2&quot; face=3D&quot;Verdana&quot;&gt;=A0=A0=A0=A0 =\r\nFilms that make a difference: &lt;a href=3D&quot;http://saraswatifilms.org/&quot; target=\r\n=3D&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://SaraswatiFilms.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div align=3D&quot